com.informix.csm

Interface IfxCsm

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Crypto, Gsscsm, IfxEncCsm, IfxGssCsm

    public interface IfxCsm
    This interface is to be implemented by all classes that are intended to be used as CSM (Communication Support Modules ) For encryption CSM we have implemented this interface in com.informix.csm.crypto.IfxEncCsm
